1. *Mladiću*, šta radiš? (Hey, young man, what are you doing?)
2. Ne znam ko je taj *mladić* koji je došao s tobom. (I don't know who that young man is who came with you.)
3. Da li si čuo za onog *mladića* koji je pre nekoliko dana osvojio nagradu? (Have you heard of that young man who won an award a few days ago?)
4. *Mladića* sam video kako trči pored reke. (I saw a young man running by the river.)
5. *Mladić* mi je dao novine na ulici. (A young man gave me a newspaper on the street.)
6. Svi su bili oduševljeni kada je *mladić* izveo neverovatan trik na skejtu. (Everyone was amazed when the young man performed an incredible trick on a skateboard.)
7. Ovaj *mladić* ima veliki potencijal za uspeh u životu. (This young man has great potential for success in life.)
8. *Mladiću*, hoćeš li da mi pomogneš da nosim ove kofere? (Hey, young man, will you help me carry these suitcases?)